r. The most recent release featured the addition of dynamic and contextual controls, sections, and panels. As WordPress 4.2 is kicking off development, core contributors are looking to add menus to the customizer for easy management from the frontend. More WordPress theme de''>WPTavern: New WordPress Customizer Import/Export Plugin Migrates Theme and Plugin Settings</a></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li class=''dashboard-news-plugin''><span>Popular Plugin:</span> <a href=''https://wordpress.org/plugins/jetpack/'' class=''dashboard-news-plugin-link''>Jetpack by WordPress.com</a>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=jetpack&amp;_wpnonce=579e2bbd31&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Jetpack by WordPress.com''>Install</a>)</span></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
