(157, 2, '2014-07-02 10:00:57', '2014-07-02 10:00:57', '<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://www.domocracy.es/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/andalucia-openfuture_.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-190" src="http://www.domocracy.es/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/andalucia-openfuture_-300x69.png" alt="andalucia-openfuture_" width="300" height="69" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://andalucia.openfuture.org/es/el_cubo#1">The Cube</a>, the first crowdworking center inside the Andalusian project <em>Open-Future</em>, is an initiative of the <em>Junta de Andalucía</em> together with Telefonica which aimed to promote entrepreneurship. Last Wednesday <em>The cube </em>opens his doors showing their facilities inside the newly restored France pavilion .</p>\r\nDomocracy could not pass up the opportunity of getting into this event and knowing the project in depth.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.domocracy.es/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Domocracy_OpenFuture_Inauguration.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-164" src="http://www.domocracy.es/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Domocracy_OpenFuture_Inauguration.jpg" alt="Domocracy_OpenFuture_Inauguration" width="600" height="337" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThe work spaces were amazing and there was a huge cube made of mirrors in the middle of the building! After the inauguration talk there was an incredible aerial silk performance inside this cube.\r\n\r\nWe hope to come back again!', 'Inauguration of "The Cube"', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'inauguration-of-the-cube', '', '', '2014-07-02 14:10:45', '2014-07-02 14:10:45', '', 0, 'http://www.domocracy.es/?p=157', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(158, 2, '2014-07-02 10:21:25', '2014-07-02 10:21:25', 'We are proud to announce that <a title="Bolt Accelerator" href="http://bolt.eu.com/es/" target="_blank">http://bolt.eu.com/es/</a> and the EOI have selected Domocracy as one of the candidate start-ups for their acceleration process. There was more than 180 participants in the process, comming from all over the world, even from Tokio and Silicon Valley! Seeing our project selected in such context of talent and innovation is just amazing, and want to thank Bolt for believing in us. We still have a long journey ahead of us, and a lot of work to do, and we are willing to walk every step of it with illusion.\r\n\r\nNext checkpoint: Bolt Inauguration the 15th of July\r\n\r\nSee you there!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Domocracy passes preselection process at Bolt Accelerator', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'domocracy-preselected-bolt', '', '', '2014-07-04 15:49:50', '2014-07-04 15:49:50', '', 0, 'http://www.domocracy.es/?p=158', 0, 'post', '', 0),
