(160, 2, '2014-07-02 11:40:03', '2014-07-02 11:40:03', '&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<a href="https://andalucia.openfuture.org/es/el_cubo#1">The Cube</a>, the first crowdworking center inside the Andalusian project <em>Open-Future</em>, is an initiative of the <em>Junta de Andalucía</em> together with Telefonica which aimed to promote entrepreneurship. Last Wednesday <em>The cube </em>opens his doors showing their facilities inside the newly restored France pavilion .\n\nDomocracy could not pass up the opportunity of getting into this event and knowing the project in depth.\n\n<a href="http://www.domocracy.es/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Domocracy_OpenFuture_Inauguration.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-164" src="http://www.domocracy.es/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Domocracy_OpenFuture_Inauguration.jpg" alt="Domocracy_OpenFuture_Inauguration" width="600" height="337" /></a>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\nThe work spaces were amazing and there was a huge cube made of mirrors in the middle of the building! After the inauguration talk there was a incredible aerial silk performance inside this cube.\n\nWe hope to come back again!', 'Inauguration of "The Cube"', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '157-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-07-02 11:40:03', '2014-07-02 11:40:03', '', 157, 'http://www.domocracy.es/157-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
