(168, 2, '2014-07-02 10:21:25', '2014-07-02 10:21:25', '<a href="http://www.domocracy.es/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Bolt-logo.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-165 aligncenter" src="http://www.domocracy.es/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Bolt-logo.jpg" alt="Bolt-logo" width="250" height="250" /></a>\r\n\r\nWe are proud to announce that <a title="Bolt Accelerator" href="http://bolt.eu.com/es/" target="_blank">http://bolt.eu.com/es/</a> and the EOI have selected Domocracy as one of the candidate start-ups for their acceleration process. There was more than 180 participants in the process, comming from all over the world, even from Tokio and Silicon Valley! Seeing our project selected in such context of talent and innovation is just amazing, and want to thank Bolt for believing in us. We still have a long journey ahead of us, and a lot of work to do, and we are willing to walk every step of it with illusion.\r\n\r\nNext checkpoint: Bolt Inauguration the 15th of July\r\n\r\nSee you there!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Domocracy passes preselection process at Bolt Accelerator', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '158-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-07-02 10:21:25', '2014-07-02 10:21:25', '', 158, 'http://www.domocracy.es/158-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
